org.mentawai.filter
Class DynamicListFilter

java.lang.Object
  org.mentawai.filter.DynamicListFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Filter
public abstract class DynamicListFilter
extends Object
implements Filter

This abstract filter is useful for placing dynamic lists in the action output so that a mtw:select cand display it. This is useful for AJAX combos that vary according to another combo.

Sergio Oliveira Jr.
